title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Jul 26 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Jul 26 2022
description:
With so many steak dinner bets, Buck suggests Clay create The Clay Travis Aged Beef Foundation, or a steakhouse. Clay is confident he will win all four steak bets he's got on the table. "Highly credible" FBI whistleblowers describe concerted effort to scuttle negative Hunter Biden stories. The Biden family is everything the media spent five years telling you the Trump family was. Buck says he is slightly overwhelmed with wedding planning. Karine Jean-Pierre slammed for claiming "economic indicators" don’t show a "recession or even a pre-recession." Matt Gaetz offends pro-abortion protesters, but owns it.
